# CLIP ChangeLog for x11-wm/openbox

*openbox-3.5.2-r5 (16 Feb 2016)

  16 Feb 2016; Tony Cheneau <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +openbox-3.5.2-r5.ebuild, -openbox-3.5.2-r4.ebuild:
  Remove migration scripts: they do not work, and it's way too ugly.

*openbox-3.5.2-r4 (18 May 2015)

  18 May 2015; Tony Cheneau <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +openbox-3.5.2-r4.ebuild,
  +files//hermes-conf-migrate.sh,
  -openbox-3.5.2-r3.ebuild:
  Add a default configuration for the clip-hermes variant: this replicate the
  default behavior of the fresh installs. This modification is protected by the
  newly reintroduced clip-hermes flag.

*openbox-3.5.2-r3 (11 Jul 2014)

  11 Jul 2014; Tony Cheneau <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +openbox-3.5.2-r3.ebuild, -openbox-3.5.2-r2.ebuild:
  Theme configuration file (when using clip-hermes) is now always loaded from
  /usr/local/share/themes/CLIP/openbox-3/themerc which is a symlink to a real
  file located in /tmp/session/openbox. This file is either a copy of a static
  themerc file or generated through a skeleton file (when configuration
  elements are presents on the system).

*openbox-3.5.2-r2 (10 Jul 2014)

  10 Jul 2014; Tony Cheneau <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +openbox-3.5.2-r2.ebuild, -openbox-3.5.2-r1.ebuild,
  +files/themerc.clip.skel:
  Add skeleton file for the importing the color of the viewer borders through an
  external configuration file.

*openbox-3.5.2-r1 (13 Jan 2014)

  13 Jan 2014; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +openbox-3.5.2-r1.ebuild, -openbox-3.5.0_p20130215-r1.ebuild,
  +files/openbox-3.5.2-gnome-session.patch,
  -files/openbox-gnome-session-3.4.9.patch,
  -files/openbox-gnomesession.patch,
  -files/openbox.desktop:
  Bump to latest.

*openbox-3.5.0_p20130215-r1 (24 May 2013)

  24 May 2013; Mickaël Salaün <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +openbox-3.5.0_p20130215-r1.ebuild, -openbox-3.5.0_p20130215.ebuild,
  files/rc.xml.clip, files/rc.xml.clip.fullscreen, files/rc.xml.clip.mix,
  files/rc.xml.clip.mixborder:
  Don't handle alt+drag but let it to clients (Vncviewer).
  Set dragThreshold to 0 pixel.

*openbox-3.5.0_p20130215 (19 Mar 2013)

  19 Mar 2013; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +openbox-3.5.0_p20130215.ebuild, -openbox-3.4.11.2-r8.ebuild,
  -files/openbox-3.4.11.2-parallel-install.patch,
  -files/openbox-3.4.7.2-clip-domains.patch,
  -files/openbox-3.4.11.2-clip-maximize.patch,
  +files/openbox-3.5.0-clip-maximize.patch,
  +files/openbox-3.5.0-clip-domains.patch:
  Bump to latest, with some minor changes :
   - Maximize patch : negate the changes introduced in OB 3.5.0
   regarding decorated/undecorated clients - let's keep things
   somewhat uncomplicated
   - Domains patch : add default (mandatory) icons for high/low
   clients in Alt+Tab focus switch popup.

