*openbox-3.4.11.2-r3 (03 Nov 2011)

  03 Nov 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +openbox-3.4.11.2-r3.ebuild, -openbox-3.4.11.2-r2.ebuild,
  +files/openbox-3.4.11.2-clip-maximize.patch,
  +files/rc.xml.clip.mixborder, files/themerc.clip:
  Support 'mixborder' mode : reduce window borders to 2pix, 
  add a patch to still add border in maximized mode, add a dedicated
  rc.xml (which retains the borders, and keeps the maximized viewer
  windows available for taskbar switch).

